  "keyFeatures": [
    "Point-of-Sale (POS) interface with cart, barcode search, and multi-payment methods (cash, QR, transfer)",
    "Full inventory management: products, categories, purchase orders, and low-stock alerts",
    "Cash register lifecycle: open/close shifts, internal movements (income/expense), and shift balancing",
    "Mobile top-up (recargas) module for Tigo, Entel, and Viva operators with wholesaler injection support",
    "Banking agent transaction module (BCP, Tigo Money, etc.) for deposits, withdrawals, and QR transfers",
    "Role-based access control (Administrador / Cajero) with JWT authentication and 45-minute inactivity timeout",
    "PDF report generation: cash movements, sales range, purchase history, inventory, and operator productivity",
    "Real-time data sync via Socket.IO (product/sale change events broadcast to all connected clients)",
    "Dashboard with ApexCharts: sales metrics, monthly target gauge, recargas donut chart, and demographic map"
  ],
